item.title: Some fun Git facts I've come across
item.description: Some fun Git facts I’ve come across Even though I don’t get to spend as much time with git as I would like, I still manage to find some interesting and fun facts I had no idea existed in the first place. Instead of jotting them down some place I would surely forget, I decided to collect them here so that I know where to find them. I’m bound to run into them sometime in the future at least…
